The paper discusses security issues related to the Internet of Things (IoT) and 3D printers, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also mentions machine learning-based algorithms, which could fall under information retrieval (cs.IR) or software engineering (cs.SE). The use of smartphones for side channel attacks could also be relevant to cyber-physical systems (cs.CY) or systems and control (cs.SY).
